      <guid isPermaLink="false">4d4c384c28370ce0e7c1408d1857db8b980b2ba9</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Jul 2025 19:23:46 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/687e93a4e33f1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/687e93a556b56.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod was inspired by Deadpanned's mods for Tears of the Kingdom and Slu's Nightmare Mode mod. It covers the Big Three: Bokoblins, Lizalfos and Moblins.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A second part will be released covering all the different types of mini-guardians.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod is intended to be used with Hyrule Rebalance and Nightmare Mode.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Shared Changes for all enemies:&lt;br&gt;Faster attack animations.&lt;br&gt;Faster detection.&lt;br&gt;Faster recovery from knockdown.&lt;br&gt;More aggression and less downtime overall.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Lizalfos have had their breath sizes slightly increased.&lt;br&gt;Certain Moblin attacks now break your guard.</description>
