      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/684b4ac335fea.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/684b4b6266324.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/684b4b7023ab3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/684b4b62d2218.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/684b4b723d55d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/684b4b70aabd6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2&gt;After the defeat of Ganon, a mysterious sword has appeared before Hyrule Castle's Sanctum. Investigation reveals the lingering spirit of Calamity Ganon trapped within the Inner Sanctum, challenging you to defeat a series of increasingly difficult waves of enemies.&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;hr&gt;This mod adds a new hidden combat shrine that may only be accessed from nearing a sword that appears in front of the sanctum after you have beaten the game. Inside, you will face a variety of corrupted and malice infused foes, taken from both the Dark Army Resurrection mod, and Relics of the Past. This fight will test your patience, endurance, skill, and strength as you battle your way to the end.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Although content from both Dark Army Resurrection and Relics of the Past are featured in this mod, it can be played completely standalone. Additionally, when trying to merge with either of the aforementioned mods, it should have a lower merge priority than them.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Added Actors&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;DgnMrgPrt_DungeonMaliceTrials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Ported Actors&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Dark Army Resurrection&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Enemy_Bokoblin_DARmalice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Enemy_Lizalfos_DARmalice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Enemy_Moriblin_DARmalice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Enemy_Lynel_DARmalice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Enemy_Lynel_Stal&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Relics of the Past&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;Enemy_Moriblin_Malice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;Enemy_Bokoblin_Malice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;Enemy_Lizalfos_Malice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;Enemy_Lynel_Gold_Ancient&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;Enemy_Guardian_Malice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;GuardianBeam_Link&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;Weapon_Sword_047&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/thetrialsofmalice.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
