      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Jun 2025 13:31:04 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683ef85a73135.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683ef85f406d7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="SelectedElement"&gt;This mod makes your Moblin mask invisible and only has its idle animation that's built into it. In order to use this, locate your update file (not within your main cemu file with the mlc1 or whatever it is) and then after finding it go to content, model, scroll till you see Armor_045.sbfres. I recommend opening a new folder on your desktop (doesn't matter where) and name it original files. Drag your original file into it and then delete the one in your update folder if it is still there. After doing so, just drag and drop the file given below into the open side part of your file folder (you should still be open in model). After that closing it, launch your game and have fun walking around the Moblin without being detected and also having the animation that's built into it!&lt;/span&gt;</description>
